				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Dinh-%E1%BB%91c/poem-WkmQ5ViHVHWdu6nUI85PMA">Dinh ốc - 營屋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/H%E1%BA%AFc-%C4%91%C3%A0m-long/poem-YIHIjqNf0VdF3XlfAs-w1w">Hắc đàm long - 黑潭龍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/L%E1%BA%A1c-th%E1%BA%A7n-ph%C3%BA/poem-ylYQnboi4bp_70hzYu0a0Q">Lạc thần phú - 洛神賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ng%C3%A2m-nguy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-_ueef2FJ_c4qmPs1m1rFXg">Ngâm nguyệt kỳ 1 - 吟月其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/Ph%C3%B9-%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-FugNf4AHWxV_jmwaGrkeCg">Phù Đổng từ - 扶董祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/author-GaA0SgEPvCmkAgLupJfzCQ">Trần Bích San</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%E1%BB%8B-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-Qu%C3%A2n/poem-LJCunKg47oyk3BhPwoLQlg">Thị Trường An Quân - 示長安君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh/poem-6y9rj-YrWsH2nTdU8zPseA">Tuý ca hành - 醉歌行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-li%C3%AAn-c%C3%BA-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-b%C3%A0i-lu%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1n-nh%E1%BB%8B-ti%C3%AAu-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-wMQlYGlF6aUupM2pBicmdQ">Tức cảnh liên cú ngũ ngôn bài luật nhất thủ, hạn “nhị tiêu” vận - 即景聯句五言排律一首，限二蕭韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Di%C3%AAn-Ni%C3%AAn/V%C5%A9-l%C3%A2m-lang/poem-9r2SL8xFgZqdSMY2iLdnmA">Vũ lâm lang - 羽林郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Di%C3%AAn-Ni%C3%AAn/author-vxx2nHLFJhKIREop8LIMDg">Tân Diên Niên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1i/poem-76D2hQ5sC9u9SnY9R16gFA">Xuất tái - 出塞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-9cGSHCUvFAIW_3kTfbKANw">Vương An Thạch</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
